WEBVTT

00:00:00.910 --> 00:00:02.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>JANUARY 9TH</b></Default>

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:03.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>20-YEAR-OLDS GATHERING VENUE</b></Default>

00:00:03.620 --> 00:00:05.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[REPORTER 1] Do you feel like
you've become an adult?</b></Default>

00:00:05.870 --> 00:00:07.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[REPORTER 2] Have you had
your first alcoholic drink yet?</b></Default>

00:00:07.750 --> 00:00:09.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Recently, Mai</b></Default>

00:00:09.199 --> 00:00:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>rumors spread
on social media are claiming</b></Default>

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:13.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you are the internet singer
Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:00:13.699 --> 00:00:15.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there any truth
to these bold claims?</b></Default>

00:00:15.699 --> 00:00:16.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen those rumors</b></Default>

00:00:17.039 --> 00:00:20.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but unfortunately, no</b></Default>

00:00:20.289 --> 00:00:22.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry
if that disappoints anyone.</b></Default>

00:00:22.289 --> 00:00:23.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you don't believe me</b></Default>

00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:26.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could show you my schedule
if that would prove it to you.</b></Default>

00:00:26.329 --> 00:00:27.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm busy enough as it is.</b></Default>

00:00:27.910 --> 00:00:29.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't possibly fit
in a music career</b></Default>

00:00:29.699 --> 00:00:31.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on top of everything else</b></Default>

00:00:31.620 --> 00:00:32.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:00:32.750 --> 00:00:35.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll have to confirm
with the higher-ups about that.</b></Default>

00:00:35.659 --> 00:00:37.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[reporters laughing]</b></Default>

00:00:38.039 --> 00:00:40.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[REPORTER 3] <i>What do you think</i>
<i>about Miss Touko Kirishima?</i></b></Default>

00:00:40.659 --> 00:00:41.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[REPORTER 4]
<i>Do you believe the rumor</i></b></Default>

00:00:41.659 --> 00:00:43.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>about dreams coming true?</i></b></Default>

00:00:44.909 --> 00:00:46.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:01:52.829 --> 00:01:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:15.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>REINDEER'S WORK</b></Default>

00:02:15.289 --> 00:02:17.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mai on TV]
<i>No, I am not Touko Kirishima.</i></b></Default>

00:02:17.500 --> 00:02:18.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>JANUARY 16TH</b></Default>

00:02:18.500 --> 00:02:19.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[REPORTER] <i>And so</b></Default>

00:02:19.789 --> 00:02:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>and official comments</i>
<i>from the agency</b></Default>

00:02:21.699 --> 00:02:23.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>they have openly denied</i>
<i>these rumors.</i></b></Default>

00:02:23.580 --> 00:02:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>But as you can see</i>
<i>by the buzz</i></b></Default>

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>generated on several</i>
<i>social media platforms</b></Default>

00:02:27.449 --> 00:02:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>there are still posts by</i>
<i>believers of the Dreaming tag</i></b></Default>

00:02:29.870 --> 00:02:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>that has gone viral.</i></b></Default>

00:02:31.659 --> 00:02:33.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now, we just need to have
the real one step forward</b></Default>

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:35.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to clear this mess up.</b></Default>

00:02:40.039 --> 00:02:40.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Good morning.</b></Default>

00:02:43.750 --> 00:02:45.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hey there. Good morning.</b></Default>

00:02:45.539 --> 00:02:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing
on the university campus today?</b></Default>

00:02:47.870 --> 00:02:49.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Attending lectures, obviously.</b></Default>

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though you're invisible?</b></Default>

00:02:51.539 --> 00:02:54.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, yeah. I am still
a college student, you know.</b></Default>

00:02:55.199 --> 00:02:57.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I saw
the Coming-of-Age day interview.</b></Default>

00:02:57.580 --> 00:02:59.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, make sure
to leave the 30th open.</b></Default>

00:03:00.580 --> 00:03:01.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like I promised</b></Default>

00:03:01.949 --> 00:03:03.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll go on that date with you.</b></Default>

00:03:09.539 --> 00:03:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hey, Toyohama.
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hypothetically</b></Default>

00:03:14.330 --> 00:03:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the scene right now</b></Default>

00:03:15.409 --> 00:03:17.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>started attending
our university tomorrow</b></Default>

00:03:17.449 --> 00:03:18.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what would you think?</b></Default>

00:03:18.789 --> 00:03:21.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, for starters</b></Default>

00:03:21.539 --> 00:03:23.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess you wouldn't.</b></Default>

00:03:23.449 --> 00:03:25.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if I wasn't conscious
of them, everywhere I go</b></Default>

00:03:25.909 --> 00:03:28.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>people would constantly
compare us as idols.</b></Default>

00:03:28.289 --> 00:03:30.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would suck if they were
pitying you on the outside.</b></Default>

00:03:30.870 --> 00:03:33.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All the while they're actually
laughing at you in their hearts.</b></Default>

00:03:33.909 --> 00:03:35.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Ow!
-You picking a fight with me?</b></Default>

00:03:35.870 --> 00:03:36.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is this?</b></Default>

00:03:37.039 --> 00:03:39.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You want to talk about
how my big sis is in the wrong?</b></Default>

00:03:39.449 --> 00:03:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you really think I'd talk
about something like that?</b></Default>

00:03:42.750 --> 00:03:45.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get the basic idea of what
you're trying to get at, though.</b></Default>

00:03:45.539 --> 00:03:46.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thing is</b></Default>

00:03:46.580 --> 00:03:49.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when I first came here</b></Default>

00:03:49.250 --> 00:03:50.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What sort of girls?</b></Default>

00:03:50.789 --> 00:03:52.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The ones that were
likely considered</b></Default>

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:54.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the prettiest girl
up until around high school.</b></Default>

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But when
they entered university</b></Default>

00:03:56.409 --> 00:03:57.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big Sis was there.</b></Default>

00:03:57.659 --> 00:03:59.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So everything became confusing.</b></Default>

00:03:59.409 --> 00:04:00.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They didn't know their place
in the world</b></Default>

00:04:00.909 --> 00:04:02.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and lost sight
of their identity.</b></Default>

00:04:02.620 --> 00:04:03.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what about you?</b></Default>

00:04:04.039 --> 00:04:05.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about me?</b></Default>

00:04:05.250 --> 00:04:07.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the president
of the Victims of Mai Club</b></Default>

00:04:07.449 --> 00:04:09.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-aren't you?
-Stop making weird clubs!</b></Default>

00:04:11.199 --> 00:04:12.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As for me</b></Default>

00:04:12.789 --> 00:04:15.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think Big Sis
is out of my reach.</b></Default>

00:04:15.159 --> 00:04:18.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if I try my best</b></Default>

00:04:18.870 --> 00:04:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big Sis lives in a completely
different world than I do</b></Default>

00:04:21.449 --> 00:04:23.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I can't even imagine it.</b></Default>

00:04:23.250 --> 00:04:24.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way I could.</b></Default>

00:04:26.699 --> 00:04:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Sakuta...</b></Default>

00:04:27.829 --> 00:04:28.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:04:29.329 --> 00:04:31.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you
to always be Big Sister's ally.</b></Default>

00:04:33.540 --> 00:04:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, of course.</b></Default>

00:04:38.410 --> 00:04:41.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>JANUARY 30TH</b></Default>

00:04:42.500 --> 00:04:44.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The story that
Santa Claus gets around</b></Default>

00:04:44.290 --> 00:04:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on a sleigh pulled by reindeer
is false, huh?</b></Default>

00:04:47.410 --> 00:04:49.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why have you been
looking outside this whole time?</b></Default>

00:04:50.079 --> 00:04:52.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was just wondering
how other people are seeing</b></Default>

00:04:52.199 --> 00:04:54.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the situation
we're in right now.</b></Default>

00:04:54.290 --> 00:04:55.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps, it looks like</b></Default>

00:04:55.329 --> 00:04:57.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the perfect
Mai Sakurajima's boyfriend</b></Default>

00:04:57.500 --> 00:04:59.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is seeing some other woman
on the down-low.</b></Default>

00:04:59.660 --> 00:05:01.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If they could
actually see you, Kirishima</b></Default>

00:05:01.620 --> 00:05:03.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>maybe they would
be thinking that.</b></Default>

00:05:03.829 --> 00:05:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah.</b></Default>

00:05:05.160 --> 00:05:07.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you happen to be dating
anybody at this time?</b></Default>

00:05:08.199 --> 00:05:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was until spring.</b></Default>

00:05:09.829 --> 00:05:10.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As I'm sure you know</b></Default>

00:05:10.910 --> 00:05:13.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even my own boyfriend
stopped perceiving me then.</b></Default>

00:05:13.500 --> 00:05:16.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] May I ask how long
you were dating that person?</b></Default>

00:05:16.750 --> 00:05:17.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Since sophomore year.</b></Default>

00:05:18.040 --> 00:05:19.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
So, you started dating back</b></Default>

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:21.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you were
in Hokkaido, right?</b></Default>

00:05:21.829 --> 00:05:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In other words</b></Default>

00:05:24.329 --> 00:05:26.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>started claiming
to be Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since it was with someone
in Hokkaido</b></Default>

00:05:29.750 --> 00:05:32.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you two had a long-distance
relationship after high school?</b></Default>

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We applied for
our university together</b></Default>

00:05:35.079 --> 00:05:36.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but he didn't get accepted</b></Default>

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:38.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even after trying for two years.</b></Default>

00:05:38.790 --> 00:05:40.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what is he doing now?</b></Default>

00:05:40.910 --> 00:05:43.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Third time's the charm</b></Default>

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:44.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He started attending
this spring.</b></Default>

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:47.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, so he put in
all that effort</b></Default>

00:05:47.079 --> 00:05:49.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then he lost his ability
to perceive you, Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:05:50.579 --> 00:05:51.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what happened.</b></Default>

00:05:52.370 --> 00:05:53.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is his major?</b></Default>

00:05:55.079 --> 00:05:56.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Statistical science.</b></Default>

00:05:57.370 --> 00:05:59.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it possible
that it's someone I know?</b></Default>

00:06:02.410 --> 00:06:03.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fukuyama, right?</b></Default>

00:06:08.449 --> 00:06:11.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does Fukuyama know that
Touko Kirishima's true identity</b></Default>

00:06:11.870 --> 00:06:13.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is Nene Iwamizawa?</b></Default>

00:06:13.660 --> 00:06:14.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] He doesn't.</b></Default>

00:06:15.329 --> 00:06:16.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But he is perceiving</b></Default>

00:06:16.500 --> 00:06:18.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the existence
of Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:06:19.329 --> 00:06:22.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So then, why isn't he able
to see you, Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Probably because
he doesn't know</b></Default>

00:06:25.579 --> 00:06:27.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I'm Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:06:27.620 --> 00:06:29.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't it more likely
that it's 'cause</b></Default>

00:06:29.410 --> 00:06:32.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're still Nene Iwamizawa
in Fukuyama's mind?</b></Default>

00:06:32.829 --> 00:06:34.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what if I am, huh?</b></Default>

00:06:35.290 --> 00:06:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here. Go buy this.</b></Default>

00:06:40.290 --> 00:06:43.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never knew Santa's presents
were procured in Motomachi.</b></Default>

00:06:43.500 --> 00:06:44.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So much for the elves.</b></Default>

00:06:45.199 --> 00:06:46.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're going to the next place.</b></Default>

00:06:53.250 --> 00:06:54.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
Where are we heading to?</b></Default>

00:06:54.660 --> 00:06:57.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A YEAR-ROUND CHRISTMAS SHOP</b></Default>

00:06:58.040 --> 00:06:58.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're here.</b></Default>

00:07:00.079 --> 00:07:01.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is it.</b></Default>

00:07:01.579 --> 00:07:03.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Looks like a house
that Santa might live in.</b></Default>

00:07:03.699 --> 00:07:04.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>328 DAYS TILL CHRISTMAS</b></Default>

00:07:04.870 --> 00:07:05.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[spring door bell rings]</b></Default>

00:07:13.750 --> 00:07:15.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Help me with finding
a tin reindeer</b></Default>

00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:17.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a palm sized one.</b></Default>

00:07:17.329 --> 00:07:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you looking for something?</b></Default>

00:07:19.449 --> 00:07:21.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does your store
have any tin reindeer?</b></Default>

00:07:21.790 --> 00:07:22.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:07:22.949 --> 00:07:24.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you mean that one.</b></Default>

00:07:25.370 --> 00:07:27.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There have been
a few people lately</b></Default>

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that have come in to buy this.</b></Default>

00:07:28.579 --> 00:07:29.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here.</b></Default>

00:07:32.829 --> 00:07:34.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:36.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That'll put an end
to our little date.</b></Default>

00:07:36.410 --> 00:07:38.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, are you giving this to me?</b></Default>

00:07:38.370 --> 00:07:40.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pass it along to Takumi, please.</b></Default>

00:07:40.290 --> 00:07:41.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on.</b></Default>

00:07:41.290 --> 00:07:43.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why don't we go hand it
to him together right now?</b></Default>

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:46.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Today's Fukuyama's birthday</b></Default>

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:48.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why
you went out of your way</b></Default>

00:07:48.449 --> 00:07:50.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to choose today, right?</b></Default>

00:07:50.699 --> 00:07:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's useless to try.</b></Default>

00:07:52.370 --> 00:07:54.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Takumi won't be able to see me.</b></Default>

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He might be able to, today.</b></Default>

00:07:56.329 --> 00:07:58.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But he couldn't</b></Default>

00:07:58.870 --> 00:08:00.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe things
will be different this time.</b></Default>

00:08:00.870 --> 00:08:02.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is none of your business!</b></Default>

00:08:03.660 --> 00:08:05.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, I really want you
to hurry up</b></Default>

00:08:05.160 --> 00:08:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and stop being invisible.</b></Default>

00:08:06.500 --> 00:08:08.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That way, you can announce</b></Default>

00:08:08.620 --> 00:08:10.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and clear up this mess.</b></Default>

00:08:10.620 --> 00:08:12.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's for your
girlfriend's sake, isn't it?</b></Default>

00:08:12.699 --> 00:08:14.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are aware
that there are people out there</b></Default>

00:08:14.750 --> 00:08:17.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that still think Mai
is Touko Kirishima, aren't you?</b></Default>

00:08:17.579 --> 00:08:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You and
your girlfriend's problems</b></Default>

00:08:19.079 --> 00:08:20.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>have nothing to do with me.</b></Default>

00:08:20.290 --> 00:08:22.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why should I have to
do something to fix it?</b></Default>

00:08:22.370 --> 00:08:24.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because the thing
you desire more than anything</b></Default>

00:08:24.540 --> 00:08:26.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is to keep being
Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:08:27.540 --> 00:08:30.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As it stands</b></Default>

00:08:30.829 --> 00:08:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lend me your smartphone.</b></Default>

00:08:32.870 --> 00:08:35.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have Fukuyama's number</b></Default>

00:08:36.330 --> 00:08:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You bought him a present
in the first place</b></Default>

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:40.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>hoping for some sort
of reaction, right?</b></Default>

00:08:40.789 --> 00:08:43.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I assume
that scarf Fukuyama wears</b></Default>

00:08:43.159 --> 00:08:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was also a present from you</b></Default>

00:08:47.500 --> 00:08:50.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's from his first birthday
after we started dating.</b></Default>

00:08:51.289 --> 00:08:52.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's so tattered.</b></Default>

00:08:52.789 --> 00:08:54.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He should just buy another one.</b></Default>

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's precious to him</b></Default>

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:58.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because it was something
his girlfriend gave him.</b></Default>

00:08:58.500 --> 00:09:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though
he can't even see me anymore?</b></Default>

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:04.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're going to complain</b></Default>

00:09:05.580 --> 00:09:06.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cell phone buzzing]</b></Default>

00:09:08.659 --> 00:09:09.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello?</b></Default>

00:09:09.659 --> 00:09:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Fukuyama?</i>
<i>It's me, Azusagawa.</i></b></Default>

00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? Hold on.</b></Default>

00:09:13.580 --> 00:09:14.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you calling me?</b></Default>

00:09:14.870 --> 00:09:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you at home right now?</b></Default>

00:09:16.750 --> 00:09:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Actually, I'm on my way</i>
<i>to the airport.</i></b></Default>

00:09:18.830 --> 00:09:21.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, are you heading back
to Hokkaido by chance?</b></Default>

00:09:21.500 --> 00:09:22.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Yeah.</i></b></Default>

00:09:22.580 --> 00:09:24.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>There is a bit</i>
<i>of trouble up there.</i></b></Default>

00:09:25.039 --> 00:09:26.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what you want?</b></Default>

00:09:26.500 --> 00:09:29.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Fukuyama, you said it's</i>
<i>your birthday today, right?</i></b></Default>

00:09:29.500 --> 00:09:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did say that.</b></Default>

00:09:31.450 --> 00:09:33.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>Then wait for me</i>
<i>at the airport.</i></b></Default>

00:09:33.330 --> 00:09:34.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>There's something</i>
<i>I'd like to give you.</i></b></Default>

00:09:37.159 --> 00:09:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, did you first meet Fukuyama
in high school?</b></Default>

00:09:40.450 --> 00:09:42.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] We went
to the same middle school too.</b></Default>

00:09:42.539 --> 00:09:44.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you like most
about Fukuyama?</b></Default>

00:09:44.659 --> 00:09:46.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've been asking
a lot of questions.</b></Default>

00:09:47.370 --> 00:09:49.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you want
to know what I think</b></Default>

00:09:49.250 --> 00:09:51.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what's great about him
is how he's never considerate</b></Default>

00:09:51.409 --> 00:09:52.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when he doesn't have to be.</b></Default>

00:09:52.789 --> 00:09:54.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He just says
whatever he wants to.</b></Default>

00:09:55.039 --> 00:09:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like what?</b></Default>

00:09:56.409 --> 00:09:59.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, for example</b></Default>

00:09:59.409 --> 00:10:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I had just met him.</b></Default>

00:10:00.789 --> 00:10:03.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was the first
to ask if I was dating Mai.</b></Default>

00:10:04.450 --> 00:10:07.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It took him forever
to finally ask me out</b></Default>

00:10:07.330 --> 00:10:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but he was always able
to do dumb stuff like that.</b></Default>

00:10:10.580 --> 00:10:11.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] For instance?</b></Default>

00:10:11.789 --> 00:10:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Back in middle school</b></Default>

00:10:13.080 --> 00:10:15.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there was a boy
that moved up from Tokyo.</b></Default>

00:10:15.950 --> 00:10:17.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rumors spread
through the entire school</b></Default>

00:10:17.909 --> 00:10:19.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that he had refused
to attend class.</b></Default>

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:21.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone was hesitant
about talking to him.</b></Default>

00:10:22.659 --> 00:10:25.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Takumi was the only one who
didn't care about any of that.</b></Default>

00:10:25.620 --> 00:10:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So he was the first one
to talk to the boy.</b></Default>

00:10:28.039 --> 00:10:30.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, wow.
That's pretty cool of him.</b></Default>

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:33.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's thanks
to that transfer student</b></Default>

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:34.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think</b></Default>

00:10:34.200 --> 00:10:36.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I really noticed Takumi.</b></Default>

00:10:36.830 --> 00:10:39.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's been going to matchmaking
parties back-to-back lately</b></Default>

00:10:39.909 --> 00:10:41.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you should give him
a proper scolding.</b></Default>

00:10:42.289 --> 00:10:44.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If Takumi can see me</b></Default>

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:47.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:50.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:10:51.039 --> 00:10:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[approaching footsteps]</b></Default>

00:10:55.289 --> 00:10:56.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow. You actually came.</b></Default>

00:10:57.039 --> 00:10:58.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What, you didn't believe me?</b></Default>

00:10:58.659 --> 00:11:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is so out of the blue.</b></Default>

00:11:00.080 --> 00:11:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought
it was some kind of joke.</b></Default>

00:11:01.789 --> 00:11:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Takumi.</b></Default>

00:11:03.080 --> 00:11:05.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, I'm sorry
you came all the way here</b></Default>

00:11:05.450 --> 00:11:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I don't really
have much time.</b></Default>

00:11:07.289 --> 00:11:08.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Listen, Takumi.</b></Default>

00:11:08.789 --> 00:11:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at me!</b></Default>

00:11:10.039 --> 00:11:11.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've gotta go screen
my carry-on luggage soon</b></Default>

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:13.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or I'll be in deep trouble.</b></Default>

00:11:14.039 --> 00:11:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Fukuyama.</b></Default>

00:11:15.409 --> 00:11:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That scarf you're wearing</b></Default>

00:11:17.039 --> 00:11:18.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you remember
who gave it to you?</b></Default>

00:11:18.870 --> 00:11:20.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who gave it to me?</b></Default>

00:11:20.370 --> 00:11:22.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, mm. Hold up.</b></Default>

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:25.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, how did I get it?</b></Default>

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:27.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen, Fukuyama</b></Default>

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:28.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you've been dating
since high school.</b></Default>

00:11:29.080 --> 00:11:31.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs] What?
Stop joking around, man.</b></Default>

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:32.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'm being serious.</b></Default>

00:11:32.700 --> 00:11:34.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a present you got
from your girlfriend.</b></Default>

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:36.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, sorry.</b></Default>

00:11:36.500 --> 00:11:38.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really don't get whatever
it is you're talking about.</b></Default>

00:11:38.659 --> 00:11:40.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's because
you've forgotten about her.</b></Default>

00:11:40.539 --> 00:11:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be more precise</b></Default>

00:11:42.330 --> 00:11:43.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to perceive her.</b></Default>

00:11:43.870 --> 00:11:46.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't remember
who gave you that scarf, right?</b></Default>

00:11:46.250 --> 00:11:47.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That proves it.</b></Default>

00:11:47.580 --> 00:11:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't remember, but still...</b></Default>

00:11:49.830 --> 00:11:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not lying to you.</b></Default>

00:11:51.580 --> 00:11:52.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really do have a girlfriend</b></Default>

00:11:52.909 --> 00:11:54.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you've been dating
since high school.</b></Default>

00:11:55.330 --> 00:11:57.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've known her
since middle school.</b></Default>

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You asked her out in your
second year of high school.</b></Default>

00:12:00.200 --> 00:12:02.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her name is Nene Iwamizawa.</b></Default>

00:12:04.200 --> 00:12:05.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, sorry</b></Default>

00:12:05.370 --> 00:12:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you're just
not making any sense, man.</b></Default>

00:12:07.580 --> 00:12:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're telling me I was really
dating a cute girl?</b></Default>

00:12:10.750 --> 00:12:12.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] That scarf
you've got on is proof.</b></Default>

00:12:13.870 --> 00:12:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh</b></Default>

00:12:15.080 --> 00:12:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to say this</b></Default>

00:12:16.250 --> 00:12:18.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'm still struggling
to follow.</b></Default>

00:12:18.580 --> 00:12:20.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really think hard about it
one more time.</b></Default>

00:12:20.659 --> 00:12:22.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[announcement] <i>Passengers for</i>
<i>Flight 555 bound for...</i></b></Default>

00:12:22.750 --> 00:12:24.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] I'm sorry, man.</b></Default>

00:12:24.200 --> 00:12:25.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I gotta get going now!</b></Default>

00:12:25.409 --> 00:12:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, Fukuyama!</b></Default>

00:12:26.539 --> 00:12:28.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know this is all
really hard to believe</b></Default>

00:12:28.500 --> 00:12:30.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I swear
that I'm telling you the truth!</b></Default>

00:12:30.409 --> 00:12:32.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry about it, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:12:32.159 --> 00:12:33.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know you're
an honest guy when it counts.</b></Default>

00:12:33.950 --> 00:12:35.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for seeing me off.</b></Default>

00:12:36.539 --> 00:12:37.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:12:37.750 --> 00:12:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, huh?</b></Default>

00:12:40.159 --> 00:12:41.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:12:44.409 --> 00:12:47.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FEBRUARY 1ST</b></Default>

00:12:49.289 --> 00:12:50.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thuds]
-[both gasp]</b></Default>

00:12:53.870 --> 00:12:54.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:12:55.450 --> 00:12:57.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know
what I'm going to do.</b></Default>

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looking pretty glum, chum.
What's wrong?</b></Default>

00:13:01.289 --> 00:13:04.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So, you go
to that driving school too, huh?</b></Default>

00:13:04.120 --> 00:13:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Already got
my provisional license.</b></Default>

00:13:06.450 --> 00:13:07.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, actually</b></Default>

00:13:07.450 --> 00:13:09.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was wanting you
to take a look at this for me.</b></Default>

00:13:10.450 --> 00:13:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ piano music playing]</b></Default>

00:13:11.580 --> 00:13:12.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing]</b></Default>

00:13:16.450 --> 00:13:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't this our university's
concert hall?</b></Default>

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:22.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's from when Nene Iwamizawa
won the Miss Campus contest.</b></Default>

00:13:23.080 --> 00:13:25.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's a segment where
they showcase their talents.</b></Default>

00:13:26.370 --> 00:13:28.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a Touko Kirishima song</b></Default>

00:13:28.909 --> 00:13:31.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI] The number of views
is amazing too.</b></Default>

00:13:31.289 --> 00:13:32.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MISS CUY CONTEST SPECIAL SKILL
SHOWCASE[NENE IWAMIZAWA]</b></Default>

00:13:32.830 --> 00:13:33.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ISN'T SHE LIKE TOUKO KIRISHIMA?</b></Default>

00:13:33.909 --> 00:13:36.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>IS IT THE ORIGINAL?
IT'S TOO GOOD.</b></Default>

00:13:36.120 --> 00:13:39.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like the last comment
on the video was made in April.</b></Default>

00:13:39.450 --> 00:13:41.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Remember what we talked about?</b></Default>

00:13:41.450 --> 00:13:43.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's when everyone
stopped perceiving her.</b></Default>

00:13:43.830 --> 00:13:44.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So...</b></Default>

00:13:44.950 --> 00:13:47.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about the same song
sung by Touko Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:13:47.909 --> 00:13:49.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yep, that'd be this one.</b></Default>

00:13:50.370 --> 00:13:51.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[same song playing]</b></Default>

00:13:53.950 --> 00:13:56.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Wow, Mito.
You really did your research.</b></Default>

00:13:56.539 --> 00:13:58.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI] It's 'cause the fact
that there's a person out there</b></Default>

00:13:58.700 --> 00:13:59.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that only you and I can see</b></Default>

00:13:59.789 --> 00:14:01.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is pretty creepy</b></Default>

00:14:01.909 --> 00:14:04.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just from listening
to this version</b></Default>

00:14:04.080 --> 00:14:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even I'm convinced that
Iwamizawa's Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:14:10.620 --> 00:14:11.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:14:11.620 --> 00:14:14.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's not
the only thing I found either.</b></Default>

00:14:15.539 --> 00:14:18.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are over a hundred videos
exactly like these ones.</b></Default>

00:14:20.289 --> 00:14:21.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TOUKO KIRISHIMA "SOMEONE" COVER</b></Default>

00:14:22.039 --> 00:14:22.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clicks]</b></Default>

00:14:23.039 --> 00:14:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing]</b></Default>

00:14:24.080 --> 00:14:26.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And every single video
has comments like</b></Default>

00:14:26.289 --> 00:14:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"You sound
just like the real deal."</b></Default>

00:14:28.080 --> 00:14:30.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though the time frame
is all over the place</b></Default>

00:14:30.200 --> 00:14:32.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at a certain point</b></Default>

00:14:32.200 --> 00:14:33.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>stop getting comments
altogether.</b></Default>

00:14:33.909 --> 00:14:35.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, you're saying
that all these people</b></Default>

00:14:35.950 --> 00:14:37.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>aren't getting perceived
anymore either?</b></Default>

00:14:40.159 --> 00:14:41.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[volume increases]</b></Default>

00:14:41.159 --> 00:14:43.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I tried to tell the director</b></Default>

00:14:43.539 --> 00:14:46.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really think we need to be
more conscious of our numbers.</b></Default>

00:14:47.409 --> 00:14:49.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, in a way</b></Default>

00:14:50.039 --> 00:14:52.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that's the case</b></Default>

00:14:52.500 --> 00:14:54.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a problem.</b></Default>

00:14:55.580 --> 00:14:57.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens, closes]</b></Default>

00:14:58.580 --> 00:15:01.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am really
in a major bind now.</b></Default>

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:02.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[phone ringing]
-Oh!</b></Default>

00:15:03.250 --> 00:15:04.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, yeah.</b></Default>

00:15:04.250 --> 00:15:05.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right, I'm coming.</b></Default>

00:15:07.450 --> 00:15:09.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes? Azusagawa here.</b></Default>

00:15:09.370 --> 00:15:10.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Oh, it's me, Fukuyama.</i></b></Default>

00:15:11.200 --> 00:15:12.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

00:15:12.200 --> 00:15:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did something happen?</b></Default>

00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:16.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Sorry about all the confusion</i>
<i>at the airport.</i></b></Default>

00:15:16.580 --> 00:15:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>In the end</b></Default>

00:15:18.159 --> 00:15:19.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>what you were trying</i>
<i>to tell me.</i></b></Default>

00:15:19.789 --> 00:15:21.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine. I wasn't bothered.</b></Default>

00:15:21.870 --> 00:15:23.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you were saying
there was some trouble?</b></Default>

00:15:23.909 --> 00:15:26.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope it wasn't anything
too serious.</b></Default>

00:15:26.120 --> 00:15:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You doing okay?</b></Default>

00:15:27.580 --> 00:15:30.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, well, I thought
I'd tell you more about that.</b></Default>

00:15:31.580 --> 00:15:32.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see</b></Default>

00:15:32.659 --> 00:15:34.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got word
from Hokkaido yesterday</b></Default>

00:15:35.000 --> 00:15:36.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that one of
my middle school classmates</b></Default>

00:15:36.870 --> 00:15:38.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>died in a traffic accident.</b></Default>

00:15:39.370 --> 00:15:41.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was it someone you knew well?</b></Default>

00:15:41.370 --> 00:15:43.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>We were pretty close</i>
<i>in middle school.</i></b></Default>

00:15:43.659 --> 00:15:46.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>He moved to my town from Tokyo</i>
<i>back in our second year.</i></b></Default>

00:15:47.080 --> 00:15:48.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I didn't want</i>
<i>to miss the funeral</b></Default>

00:15:48.620 --> 00:15:50.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>so I was kind of rushing.</i></b></Default>

00:15:51.039 --> 00:15:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>No. Sorry I bothered you.</i></b></Default>

00:15:53.330 --> 00:15:55.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Were you able</i>
<i>to give a proper farewell?</i></b></Default>

00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:56.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:15:56.289 --> 00:15:58.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I started bawling
midway through</b></Default>

00:15:58.289 --> 00:16:01.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and all my old classmates
totally saw and laughed at me.</b></Default>

00:16:01.539 --> 00:16:03.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you called
just to tell me that?</b></Default>

00:16:03.909 --> 00:16:05.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Well, there was that too but...</i></b></Default>

00:16:06.289 --> 00:16:07.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I heard something</i>
<i>really strange</i></b></Default>

00:16:07.750 --> 00:16:09.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>from the classmates</i>
<i>that gathered there.</i></b></Default>

00:16:09.830 --> 00:16:11.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something strange?</b></Default>

00:16:11.250 --> 00:16:12.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>About #Dreaming.</i></b></Default>

00:16:13.000 --> 00:16:15.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Apparently, my friend</i>
<i>that got in the accident</b></Default>

00:16:15.580 --> 00:16:18.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>he didn't have a dream</i>
<i>on the night of Christmas Eve.</i></b></Default>

00:16:18.289 --> 00:16:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:16:19.330 --> 00:16:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>You know how people believe</i></b></Default>

00:16:20.450 --> 00:16:22.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>that the dreams are like</i>
<i>windows into the future?</i></b></Default>

00:16:23.370 --> 00:16:24.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>So, they came up with the idea</i></b></Default>

00:16:24.870 --> 00:16:26.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>that the fact he didn't</i>
<i>have a dream was...</i></b></Default>

00:16:27.200 --> 00:16:29.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>because he was dead</i>
<i>in the future.</i></b></Default>

00:16:29.830 --> 00:16:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I... I'm sure</i>
<i>there's no way it's true</b></Default>

00:16:31.789 --> 00:16:33.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>but I thought you'd mentioned</i></b></Default>

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:34.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Sakurajima didn't</i>
<i>have a dream either</b></Default>

00:16:34.909 --> 00:16:36.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>so I thought</i>
<i>I should let you know.</i></b></Default>

00:16:38.409 --> 00:16:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I don't think
that's the case</b></Default>

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:42.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but thank you very much
for informing me.</b></Default>

00:16:42.750 --> 00:16:44.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Uh, why are you being</i>
<i>so polite?</i></b></Default>

00:16:44.700 --> 00:16:45.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because, Fukuyama</b></Default>

00:16:46.039 --> 00:16:47.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm the type
that respects my elders.</b></Default>

00:16:47.950 --> 00:16:48.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Huh?</i></b></Default>

00:16:48.950 --> 00:16:51.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all, you are older
than me, aren't you?</b></Default>

00:16:51.500 --> 00:16:52.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By two years?</b></Default>

00:16:52.659 --> 00:16:54.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>How'd you figure that out?</i>
<i>I didn't say anything!</i></b></Default>

00:16:54.870 --> 00:16:56.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I heard it</i>
<i>from a certain someone</i></b></Default>

00:16:56.539 --> 00:16:58.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>that knows you very intimately.</i></b></Default>

00:16:58.200 --> 00:16:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, could that person be</b></Default>

00:16:59.950 --> 00:17:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the supposed girlfriend
that you were trying</b></Default>

00:17:01.580 --> 00:17:03.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to tell me I had at the airport?</b></Default>

00:17:03.370 --> 00:17:04.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Yes.</i></b></Default>

00:17:04.369 --> 00:17:05.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

00:17:05.450 --> 00:17:08.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I really have forgotten
something important, huh?</b></Default>

00:17:08.829 --> 00:17:11.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're really starting
to believe what I told you</b></Default>

00:17:11.289 --> 00:17:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>please do whatever it takes
to remember her.</b></Default>

00:17:13.660 --> 00:17:14.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Fukuyama</b></Default>

00:17:14.660 --> 00:17:17.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>your girlfriend also said</i>
<i>that she didn't have a dream.</i></b></Default>

00:17:17.329 --> 00:17:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

00:17:18.369 --> 00:17:20.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>She may be in</i>
<i>a dangerous situation as well.</i></b></Default>

00:17:21.289 --> 00:17:22.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

00:17:22.410 --> 00:17:23.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Seriously.</i></b></Default>

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, of course, my mind is
filled with thoughts of Mai.</b></Default>

00:17:26.950 --> 00:17:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I'll leave your girlfriend
up to you.</b></Default>

00:17:29.539 --> 00:17:30.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>If I do something about it</b></Default>

00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:33.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>do you promise to stop with</i>
<i>that creepy, polite talk?</i></b></Default>

00:17:33.750 --> 00:17:35.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I promise you.</b></Default>

00:17:35.289 --> 00:17:36.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>That gives me some motivation.</i></b></Default>

00:17:37.369 --> 00:17:38.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I'll see you later.</i></b></Default>

00:17:42.000 --> 00:17:43.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[line ringing]</b></Default>

00:17:44.789 --> 00:17:47.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[clicks]
-[MAI] <i>Sakuta? What's wrong?</i></b></Default>

00:17:47.450 --> 00:17:48.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Oh, Mai.
<i>-What?</i></b></Default>

00:17:48.869 --> 00:17:50.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[voice trembling]
I want to see you right now.</b></Default>

00:17:50.700 --> 00:17:52.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Oh, what perfect timing.</i></b></Default>

00:17:52.539 --> 00:17:53.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell rings]</b></Default>

00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:57.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Now open the door.</i>
<i>It's cold out here.</i></b></Default>

00:17:59.410 --> 00:18:00.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[approaching footsteps]</b></Default>

00:18:01.829 --> 00:18:03.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the matter with you?</b></Default>

00:18:04.950 --> 00:18:05.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Mai.</b></Default>

00:18:11.539 --> 00:18:12.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's going on?</b></Default>

00:18:13.289 --> 00:18:14.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I promise, Mai</b></Default>

00:18:15.039 --> 00:18:16.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will protect you.</b></Default>

00:18:17.579 --> 00:18:19.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Then I promise, Sakuta</b></Default>

00:18:19.500 --> 00:18:21.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll protect you too.</b></Default>

00:18:21.200 --> 00:18:22.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

00:18:23.829 --> 00:18:24.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone clicks]</b></Default>

00:18:25.250 --> 00:18:27.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[AUTOMATED VOICE] <i>Connecting</i>
<i>to voicemail service.</i></b></Default>

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:28.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[beeps]</b></Default>

00:18:29.039 --> 00:18:29.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SANTA</b></Default>

00:18:30.039 --> 00:18:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I called</i>
<i>because there's something</i></b></Default>

00:18:31.500 --> 00:18:32.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I'd like you</i>
<i>to help me out with.</i></b></Default>

00:18:33.039 --> 00:18:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>On February 3rd, please come</i>
<i>to the following location.</i></b></Default>

00:18:36.579 --> 00:18:38.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Kanazawa district</i>
<i>of Yokohama...</i></b></Default>

00:18:39.750 --> 00:18:43.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FEBRUARY 3RD</b></Default>

00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:46.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think this is the right place.</b></Default>

00:18:46.539 --> 00:18:48.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell rings]</b></Default>

00:18:48.369 --> 00:18:51.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>01 IWAMIZAWA</b></Default>

00:18:52.079 --> 00:18:54.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, I came here
just like you asked.</b></Default>

00:18:55.329 --> 00:18:58.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here. Throw those away
downstairs for me, okay?</b></Default>

00:18:58.619 --> 00:18:59.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

00:19:09.200 --> 00:19:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell rings]</b></Default>

00:19:12.950 --> 00:19:14.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Took you long enough.</b></Default>

00:19:14.410 --> 00:19:16.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wouldn't you normally start
by saying thanks first?</b></Default>

00:19:17.289 --> 00:19:19.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks. You're a lifesaver.</b></Default>

00:19:19.500 --> 00:19:20.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That, and also</b></Default>

00:19:20.869 --> 00:19:22.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should you be
throwing this away?</b></Default>

00:19:22.410 --> 00:19:23.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>MISS CUY CONTEST
64TH GRAND PRIZE</b></Default>

00:19:23.869 --> 00:19:26.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wasn't this something
precious to you, Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:19:26.579 --> 00:19:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you talking about?</b></Default>

00:19:28.829 --> 00:19:30.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hurry up and come inside.</b></Default>

00:19:31.079 --> 00:19:32.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

00:19:38.369 --> 00:19:39.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm? [gasps]</b></Default>

00:19:50.250 --> 00:19:52.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not gonna stand there
all day, are you?</b></Default>

00:19:52.369 --> 00:19:54.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, sit down. I need you
to help me build this thing.</b></Default>

00:19:55.500 --> 00:19:58.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aren't boys supposed to be good
with this kind of stuff?</b></Default>

00:19:58.200 --> 00:20:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think there are probably guys
who aren't good at it too.</b></Default>

00:20:05.000 --> 00:20:06.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know how the dreaming tag</b></Default>

00:20:06.410 --> 00:20:08.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>caused a big deal online
last Christmas?</b></Default>

00:20:08.869 --> 00:20:10.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about it?</b></Default>

00:20:10.160 --> 00:20:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Kirishima</b></Default>

00:20:11.579 --> 00:20:13.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you told me that
you didn't have a dream.</b></Default>

00:20:13.619 --> 00:20:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Yeah, just like
your girlfriend, you said.</b></Default>

00:20:16.869 --> 00:20:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I happened to hear
a strange rumor.</b></Default>

00:20:19.500 --> 00:20:21.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently, the people
who didn't have a dream</b></Default>

00:20:21.539 --> 00:20:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>didn't have them because
they didn't exist in the future.</b></Default>

00:20:25.410 --> 00:20:26.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That would mean...</b></Default>

00:20:27.119 --> 00:20:28.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're dead by that point.</b></Default>

00:20:30.410 --> 00:20:32.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's not just a rumor.</b></Default>

00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:34.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There really was
someone who died.</b></Default>

00:20:35.329 --> 00:20:36.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Is it someone you know?</b></Default>

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:38.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] No.
It's someone you know.</b></Default>

00:20:39.500 --> 00:20:40.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back in middle school</b></Default>

00:20:40.869 --> 00:20:43.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there was a boy
who moved up from Tokyo, right?</b></Default>

00:20:43.500 --> 00:20:45.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know
about anyone like that.</b></Default>

00:20:45.539 --> 00:20:47.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fukuyama was in a rush
at the airport</b></Default>

00:20:47.789 --> 00:20:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so he could
hurry back to Hokkaido</b></Default>

00:20:49.289 --> 00:20:51.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and attend
that person's funeral.</b></Default>

00:20:51.160 --> 00:20:52.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And who is this Fukuyama?</b></Default>

00:20:52.910 --> 00:20:53.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, what?</b></Default>

00:20:53.910 --> 00:20:56.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, Takumi Fukuyama.
He's your boyfriend.</b></Default>

00:20:56.700 --> 00:20:58.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no idea
who you're talking about.</b></Default>

00:20:58.910 --> 00:21:00.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's someone you've been dating</b></Default>

00:21:00.160 --> 00:21:01.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since back
when you lived in Hokkaido.</b></Default>

00:21:01.619 --> 00:21:03.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm telling you</b></Default>

00:21:03.700 --> 00:21:05.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I'm telling you</b></Default>

00:21:05.369 --> 00:21:07.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the guy you dated
as Nene Iwamizawa.</b></Default>

00:21:07.700 --> 00:21:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now another name
I don't recognize.</b></Default>

00:21:09.829 --> 00:21:10.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:21:11.829 --> 00:21:14.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, who is this Iwamizawa?</b></Default>

00:21:16.910 --> 00:21:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean?
That's your name!</b></Default>

00:21:20.079 --> 00:21:22.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What have you been talking about
this entire time?</b></Default>

00:21:23.039 --> 00:21:26.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My name is Touko Kirishima.
I've already told you that.</b></Default>

00:21:31.700 --> 00:21:32.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] <i>Sounds like</i>
<i>you're dealing with</i></b></Default>

00:21:32.869 --> 00:21:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>another strange course</i>
<i>of events.</i></b></Default>

00:21:35.079 --> 00:21:37.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I know.
That's why I'm consulting you.</b></Default>

00:21:37.660 --> 00:21:39.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>First things first.</i></b></Default>

00:21:39.200 --> 00:21:40.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Let's talk about</i>
<i>the Santa Claus room.</i></b></Default>

00:21:41.039 --> 00:21:43.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just now, Himeji told me that</b></Default>

00:21:43.160 --> 00:21:45.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's always items that have
something to do with Christmas</b></Default>

00:21:45.789 --> 00:21:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>on the screen</i>
<i>in Touko Kirishima videos.</i></b></Default>

00:21:50.500 --> 00:21:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Perhaps Nene Iwamizawa</i>
<i>caught note of that</i></b></Default>

00:21:53.369 --> 00:21:55.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>and started collecting</i>
<i>those same items.</i></b></Default>

00:21:55.329 --> 00:21:56.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] For what purpose?</b></Default>

00:21:57.329 --> 00:21:59.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>To become Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

00:22:00.410 --> 00:22:01.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>If you were Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

00:22:01.910 --> 00:22:04.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>it would be a contradiction</i>
<i>not to have the belongings</i></b></Default>

00:22:04.250 --> 00:22:05.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>that you should own</b></Default>

00:22:05.700 --> 00:22:06.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well...</b></Default>

00:22:06.910 --> 00:22:09.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And if she really is
that particular</b></Default>

00:22:09.160 --> 00:22:11.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about being Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

